                  </hi>. I live in Gray's Inn-lane. I was in Gray's Inn-lane, and <hi rend="smallCaps">SAW</hi> the prisoners three or four times, walking backwards and forwards, and looking at my window—I saw Wakefield put his hand in through the broken pane, but he did not get any thing out—I went to the corner of Gray's Inn<lb></lb>gate, and had a full view of them there—I saw them all walk back—one of the little ones put his hand in, and then they walked off—Ward rushed out of my shop, and I went to his assistance—this cock is my property.</p>
